      <abstract encodinganalog="520$a" label="Abstract: ">
                    Papers of the American author, dramatist, novelist, poet, and short story writer.  
Collection includes typescript and holograph writings, including book manuscripts, essays, plays, 
poems, short stories, and notebooks.  Also, some family material, such as writings, clippings, 
memorabilia, a scrapbook, and correspondence, including letters from Theodore Roosevelt to Judge and 
Mrs. Andrews.</abstract>
